      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE EMU (1) is a sprinter who excels over the short dashes. Was a strong winner last time (17.38) over 300m at this track in a Grade 6. Form at the trip strong including one wins. Has a strong record out of this box with two wins and a minor placing from four starts. Hard to go past. POTENT CREW (2) had been racing well without winning, recording five minors on end before copping a check in the run and finishing seventh in a Grade 4/5 at this track (23.41). Should be in this for a long way. RIPPLE RHYTHM (3) was below latest but prior to that a Grade 6 winner in quick time (17.66) at this track in a Grade 6. Well placed here and should do much better. AKRON ROCKET (4) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
